Santa Wants No Witness was made for the Winter Game Jam 2022 organized by Game Development Club, IIT Kanpur.
Programmer: Aryan M
Artist: Depanshu S
Checkout our game at https://aryanmaurya383.itch.io/santa-wants-no-witness.
Checkout our gameplay on youtube at https://youtu.be/OaIrEl2n8K0. 
Hope you like it.
Enjoy!!

